author: kwsutter
msg: Resolving JIRA report OPENJPA-63 for better pessimistic lock support for DB2.  Instead of the usual "for update" clause, db2 dictionary will now use "with rr use and keep update locks" clause.
A couple of additional changes were necessary to properly detect the version of DB2 currently in use.
